data.description: Need some space? Check out this beauty! 5+bedrooms, Loft, 3.1 Bathrooms, Full finished basement with in-law arrangement: Full bedroom and bathroom, 2nd kitchen, 2nd laundry room, living room, bonus room, and plenty of storage space. Main floor is open with a light and bright flow with Brazilian cherry hardwood, and nice views out to a gorgeous backyard. The powder room was redone in 2022 and you will love the huge main floor laundry/mud room off the 3-car garage with sink. Upstairs has 4 generously sized bedroom 3 with walk-in closets and a huge loft area. The Master suite is truly a luxury getaway with lots of space, gleaming hardwood flooring, ceiling fan, walk-in closet with built-in organization. The spa-like master bath has heated flooring, custom cabinetry and tile work, luxury bath and shower you won't want to leave. Your backyard has a new pool and composite deck 2022 and 2023 that you can enjoy this summer. Along with a nice patio, fire-pit, custom made garden, and shed in this large fenced in yard. Recent updates include: all new lighting, garage door openers, hot water tank and filtration, kitchen fridge. Hot water tank has pressure pump, so you will never run out of hot water. Roof and siding is estimated at 4-5 years old.
